data.meta_description: Born in Eschdorf, Germany. Carl's occupation was that of a miller. Home: Altenburg, Brazeau (township), Perry, Missouri  Carl Gottlieb Zeibig age 28, Henriette Wilhelmine age 25, and Karl August age 2 came from Germany on the Olbers which docked in New Orleans.
